      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented here is an automotive specimen of unparalleled caliber. This vehicle remains in showroom condition, having been curated and maintained to the most exacting standards. With an exterior that retains its original factory luster and an interior entirely devoid of discernible wear, this offering represents the pinnacle of pre-owned excellence. It is, without reservation, a definitive acquisition for the discerning enthusiast who demands nothing short of perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
