    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have got to see this absolute beauty. I\u2019ve taken such good care of her\u2014she honestly looks and drives like she just rolled off the showroom floor! There isn't a scratch or a dent to be found, and the interior is still smelling totally fresh. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s time for someone else to enjoy this flawless ride. You won\u2019t find another one in such incredible shape, I promise!",
