    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Presenting an investment-grade FD3S Mazda RX-7, a masterclass in lightweight engineering and rotary performance. This example features the sequentially turbocharged 13B-REW power plant, maintaining exceptional compression and thermal efficiency. The chassis remains structurally flawless, retaining its factory-tuned 50:50 weight distribution and aluminum double-wishbone suspension geometry. Every mechanical component, from the Torsen limited-slip differential to the synchronizers in the five-speed manual gearbox, operates with surgical precision. Free from the typical vacuum line degradation or interior bolster wear, this showroom-quality specimen represents the pinnacle of 90s JDM design.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
