    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting an absolutely flawless 2020 Porsche 718 Cayman in GT Silver Metallic. This vehicle has been fastidiously maintained in a climate-controlled environment and has never seen a drop of rain. The exterior boasts a professional-grade ceramic coating, ensuring the paint remains deep and reflective with zero swirl marks or stone chips. Inside, the Bordeaux Red leather interior remains in showroom condition; the bolsters show no signs of entry wear, and the cabin still retains that distinctive new-car aroma. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a full service history exclusively through Porsche authorized centers. Every button, switch, and system functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a true collector-grade example for the discerning enthusiast who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
